    "name": {
      "zh": "Crye Precision JPC 插板胸挂（复合迷彩）",
      "en": "Crye Precision JPC Plate Carrier (MultiCam)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "JPC",
      "en": "JPC"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "备受赞誉的伞降行动插板胸挂 (JPC) 在设计之初就考虑到了重量与外形控制问题，以尽可能不影响穿戴者的行动。其模块化系统允许使用者自行定制配装，并根据任务需求快速调整附件。由 Crye Precision 公司设计制造，复合迷彩版本。",
      "en": "The widely beloved Jumpable Plate Carrier (JPC) was designed to maximize operator mobility by reducing weight and bulk. Its modular system allows for personalized loadouts and quick gear adjustments depending on the mission. Manufactured by Crye Precision. MultiCam version."
    },
